---
import SectionLabel from './SectionLabel.astro';
---

<section id="probleme" class="section pain-points">
  <div class="glow glow--cyan" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="glow glow--pink" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <SectionLabel text="Kommt dir bekannt vor?" />

    <div class="pain__grid">
      <!-- Left: Accordion Headlines (+ mobile accordion bodies) -->
      <div class="pain__headings">
        <button class="pain__heading pain__heading--active" data-pain="1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="pain-accordion-1">
          <span class="pain__num">01</span>
          <span class="pain__heading-text">Budget flie&szlig;t &mdash; Ergebnisse nicht.</span>
          <span class="pain__arrow">&rarr;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="pain__accordion-body" data-pain-body="1" id="pain-accordion-1">
          <p class="pain__accordion-text">Zu wenig Anfragen trotz laufender Kampagnen? Das Problem ist selten das Budget &mdash; sondern fehlende Attribution.</p>
          <div class="pain__stat">
            <span class="pain__stat-number">72%</span>
            <span class="pain__stat-label">der KMU k&ouml;nnen den ROI nicht messen</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button class="pain__heading" data-pain="2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="pain-accordion-2">
          <span class="pain__num">02</span>
          <span class="pain__heading-text">Viele Kan&auml;le, keine Strategie.</span>
          <span class="pain__arrow">&rarr;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="pain__accordion-body" data-pain-body="2" id="pain-accordion-2">
          <p class="pain__accordion-text">5 Kan&auml;le parallel, alle halbherzig. Kein Funnel, kein Fokus, kein roter Faden.</p>
          <div class="pain__stat">
            <span class="pain__stat-number">5&times;</span>
            <span class="pain__stat-label">h&ouml;herer ROI bei fokussierten 2&ndash;3 Kan&auml;len</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button class="pain__heading" data-pain="3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="pain-accordion-3">
          <span class="pain__num">03</span>
          <span class="pain__heading-text">Besucher kommen &mdash; aber niemand konvertiert.</span>
          <span class="pain__arrow">&rarr;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="pain__accordion-body" data-pain-body="3" id="pain-accordion-3">
          <p class="pain__accordion-text">Traffic ist da &mdash; aber keine Anfragen. Langsame Seiten, unklare CTAs und Landingpages die nicht konvertieren.</p>
          <div class="pain__stat">
            <span class="pain__stat-number">3&times;</span>
            <span class="pain__stat-label">mehr Leads durch CRO als durch Budget-Verdreifachung</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button class="pain__heading" data-pain="4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="pain-accordion-4">
          <span class="pain__num">04</span>
          <span class="pain__heading-text">Dein Dashboard zeigt dir ein falsches Bild.</span>
          <span class="pain__arrow">&rarr;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="pain__accordion-body" data-pain-body="4" id="pain-accordion-4">
          <p class="pain__accordion-text">ROAS sieht gut aus, Marge nicht. AdBlocker und iOS-Updates schlucken bis zu 40% deiner Daten.</p>
          <div class="pain__stat">
            <span class="pain__stat-number">20&ndash;40%</span>
            <span class="pain__stat-label">der Conversions gehen durch Browser-Restriktionen verloren</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button class="pain__heading" data-pain="5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="pain-accordion-5">
          <span class="pain__num">05</span>
          <span class="pain__heading-text">Kein Team, keine Zeit, kein Plan.</span>
          <span class="pain__arrow">&rarr;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="pain__accordion-body" data-pain-body="5" id="pain-accordion-5">
          <p class="pain__accordion-text">Marketing passiert &bdquo;nebenbei&ldquo; &mdash; und bringt nebenbei-Ergebnisse. Eine Agentur gibt dir ein ganzes Team.</p>
          <div class="pain__stat">
            <span class="pain__stat-number">3&times;</span>
            <span class="pain__stat-label">schnelleres Wachstum bei strategischem Outsourcing</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Expandable Content Panels -->
      <div class="pain__content">

        <!-- Panel 1: Budget ohne Ergebnis -->
        <div class="pain__panel pain__panel--active" data-panel="1">
          <h3 class="pain__panel-title">Du investierst &mdash; aber dein Umsatz bewegt sich nicht.</h3>
          <p class="pain__panel-text">Google Ads l&auml;uft, Social Media wird bespielt, vielleicht sogar SEO beauftragt. Trotzdem kommen zu wenig Anfragen. Das Problem ist selten das Budget &mdash; sondern dass niemand misst, welcher Euro Umsatz bringt und welcher verbrennt.</p>
          <p class="pain__panel-text">Ohne klare Attribution gibst du mehr aus f&uuml;r den gleichen Effekt. Die Kampagnen sehen im Dashboard gut aus &mdash; aber am Kontostand merkst du nichts davon.</p>
          <div class="pain__callout">
            <span class="pain__callout-label">Typisches Muster:</span> 3.000&ndash;10.000&nbsp;&euro;/Monat Adspend, steigende Klickkosten, sinkende Conversion-Rate &mdash; und keiner kann erkl&auml;ren, warum.
          </div>
          <div class="pain__stat">
            <span class="pain__stat-number">72%</span>
            <span class="pain__stat-label">der KMU k&ouml;nnen den ROI ihrer Marketing-Ma&szlig;nahmen nicht zuverl&auml;ssig messen. <span class="pain__stat-source">(HubSpot, 2024)</span></span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Panel 2: Kein Fokus -->
        <div class="pain__panel" data-panel="2">
          <h3 class="pain__panel-title">Alles ein bisschen &mdash; aber nichts richtig.</h3>
          <p class="pain__panel-text">Instagram am Montag, Google-Ad am Dienstag, Newsletter am Freitag. Klingt nach Marketing &mdash; ist aber Aktivit&auml;t ohne Strategie. Ohne klaren Fokus entsteht Marketing-Wildwuchs: viel Aufwand, wenig Wirkung.</p>
          <p class="pain__panel-text">Jeder Kanal performt mittelm&auml;&szlig;ig, keiner richtig. Du kannst nie sagen, was funktioniert und was weg kann &mdash; also machst du weiter alles und verschwendest Ressourcen.</p>
          <div class="pain__callout">
            <span class="pain__callout-label">Kernproblem:</span> Kein Funnel, kein Fokus, kein System. 5 Kan&auml;le parallel, alle halbherzig &mdash; jede Woche neue Ideen, aber kein roter Faden.
          </div>
          <div class="pain__stat">
            <span class="pain__stat-number">5&times;</span>
            <span class="pain__stat-label">h&ouml;herer ROI bei Unternehmen, die fokussiert 2&ndash;3 Kan&auml;le bespielen statt 6+ halbherzig. <span class="pain__stat-source">(McKinsey, 2024)</span></span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Panel 3: UX / Keine Conversions -->
        <div class="pain__panel" data-panel="3">
          <h3 class="pain__panel-title">Deine Website hat Traffic &mdash; aber keinen Umsatz.</h3>
          <p class="pain__panel-text">Anzeigen liefern Klicks, SEO bringt Besucher, Social Media generiert Reichweite. Aber am Monatsende stehen kaum Anfragen in der Pipeline. Das Problem sitzt nicht im Marketing &mdash; sondern auf deiner Website.</p>
          <p class="pain__panel-text">Langsame Ladezeiten, unklare CTAs und Landingpages die f&uuml;r alle sprechen und deshalb f&uuml;r niemanden. 60&ndash;80&nbsp;% deiner Besucher sind nach 10 Sekunden wieder weg.</p>
          <div class="pain__callout">
            <span class="pain__callout-label">Die Rechnung:</span> 1.000 Besucher &times; 1&nbsp;% Conversion = 10 Leads. Durch CRO auf 3&nbsp;% werden daraus 30 &mdash; ohne einen Euro mehr Adspend.
          </div>
          <div class="pain__stat">
            <span class="pain__stat-number">3&times;</span>
            <span class="pain__stat-label">mehr Leads durch Conversion-Optimierung als durch Verdreifachung des Werbebudgets. <span class="pain__stat-source">(Unbounce, 2024)</span></span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Panel 4: Falsches Dashboard -->
        <div class="pain__panel" data-panel="4">
          <h3 class="pain__panel-title">Deine Zahlen sehen gut aus &mdash; dein Konto nicht.</h3>
          <p class="pain__panel-text">Dein Dashboard zeigt ROAS von 4x, aber deine Marge sagt etwas anderes. AdBlocker, iOS-Updates und Cookie-Consent schlucken bis zu 40&nbsp;% deiner Daten. Algorithmen trainieren auf falschen Zahlen und optimieren in die falsche Richtung.</p>
          <p class="pain__panel-text">Einmal eingerichtetes Tracking hei&szlig;t nicht: f&uuml;r immer korrekt. Consent-Mode-Updates und Pixel-Migrationen erzeugen stille Datenl&uuml;cken. Die Kampagnen laufen weiter &mdash; auf falscher Grundlage.</p>
          <div class="pain__callout">
            <span class="pain__callout-label">Beispiel:</span> Bei 5.000&nbsp;&euro;/Monat Adspend und 35&nbsp;% fehlendem Signal verbrennst du ~1.750&nbsp;&euro; monatlich &mdash; nicht durch schlechte Kampagnen, durch fehlende Daten.
          </div>
          <div class="pain__stat">
            <span class="pain__stat-number">20&ndash;40%</span>
            <span class="pain__stat-label">der Conversion-Daten gehen durch Browser-Restriktionen und Cookie-Consent verloren. <span class="pain__stat-source">(Stape.io, 2025)</span></span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Panel 5: Kein Team -->
        <div class="pain__panel" data-panel="5">
          <h3 class="pain__panel-title">Marketing passiert nebenbei &mdash; und bringt nebenbei-Ergebnisse.</h3>
          <p class="pain__panel-text">In den meisten KMU macht der Gesch&auml;ftsf&uuml;hrer oder ein Werkstudent &bdquo;auch Marketing&ldquo;. Kampagnen starten, wenn Umsatz sinkt. Content entsteht, wenn Zeit bleibt. Optimierung passiert nie.</p>
          <p class="pain__panel-text">Einen In-house-Marketer einstellen kostet 45.000&ndash;65.000&nbsp;&euro;/Jahr &mdash; und deckt trotzdem nur einen Bruchteil ab: Ads, Analytics, Design, CRO, Strategie. Eine Agentur gibt dir ein ganzes Team.</p>
          <div class="pain__callout pain__callout--pink">
            <span class="pain__callout-label">Realit&auml;t:</span> 68&nbsp;% der KMU im DACH-Raum haben keine eigene Marketing-Abteilung. Marketing wird neben dem Tagesgesch&auml;ft erledigt &mdash; oder gar nicht.
          </div>
          <div class="pain__stat">
            <span class="pain__stat-number">3&times;</span>
            <span class="pain__stat-label">schnelleres Wachstum bei KMU, die Marketing strategisch auslagern statt intern mitzumachen. <span class="pain__stat-source">(Deloitte, 2024)</span></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Transition: Die Lösung -->
    <div class="pain__solution reveal" id="tracking-first">
      <div class="pain__solution-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <h2 class="pain__solution-heading">Die L&ouml;sung: <span class="text-cyan">Klarheit vor Budget.</span></h2>
      <p class="pain__solution-text">Bevor wir einen Euro in Ads investieren, analysieren wir, was wirklich funktioniert. Sauberes Tracking, klare Strategie, ein Team das liefert &mdash; und erst dann skalieren.</p>
      <a href="#kontakt" class="pain__solution-cta" data-magnetic>Kostenloses Audit anfragen &rarr;</a>
      <div class="pain__solution-deco" aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="hex hex--1"></span>
        <span class="hex hex--2"></span>
        <span class="hex hex--3"></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
(function () {
  const headings = document.querySelectorAll('.pain__heading');
  const panels = document.querySelectorAll('.pain__panel');
  if (!headings.length) return;

  const isMobile = window.matchMedia('(max-width: 768px)');

  function activate(index) {
    headings.forEach(h => h.classList.remove('pain__heading--active'));
    panels.forEach(p => p.classList.remove('pain__panel--active'));
    headings[index]?.classList.add('pain__heading--active');
    panels[index]?.classList.add('pain__panel--active');
  }

  function toggleMobileAccordion(index) {
    const heading = headings[index];
    const isActive = heading.classList.contains('pain__heading--active');
    // Close all
    headings.forEach(h => {
      h.classList.remove('pain__heading--active');
      h.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
    });
    // Toggle clicked
    if (!isActive) {
      heading.classList.add('pain__heading--active');
      heading.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'true');
    }
  }

  headings.forEach((heading, i) => {
    heading.addEventListener('click', () => {
      if (isMobile.matches) {
        toggleMobileAccordion(i);
      } else {
        activate(i);
      }
    });
    heading.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => {
      if (!isMobile.matches) activate(i);
    });
    heading.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
      if (e.key === 'Enter' || e.key === ' ') {
        e.preventDefault();
        if (isMobile.matches) {
          toggleMobileAccordion(i);
        } else {
          activate(i);
        }
      }
    });
  });

  // Re-sync desktop panels when viewport crosses mobile breakpoint
  isMobile.addEventListener('change', (e) => {
    if (!e.matches) {
      const activeIndex = [...headings].findIndex(h =>
        h.classList.contains('pain__heading--active')
      );
      activate(activeIndex >= 0 ? activeIndex : 0);
    }
  });
})();
</script>

<style>
  .pain-points { position: relative; overflow: hidden; }

  .pain__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .pain__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
      align-items: start;
    }
  }

  /* ===== Left: Headings ===== */
  .pain__headings {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .pain__heading {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.15rem 0;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    cursor: pointer;
    text-align: left;
    width: 100%;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    color: inherit;
    font: inherit;
  }
  .pain__heading:first-child {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .pain__num {
    font: 700 0.7rem/1 var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--text-faint);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }
  .pain__heading--active .pain__num {
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
  }

  .pain__heading-text {
    flex: 1;
    font: 700 clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.35rem)/1.25 var(--font-heading);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }
  .pain__heading--active .pain__heading-text {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  .pain__heading:hover .pain__heading-text {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .pain__arrow {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: transparent;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .pain__heading--active .pain__arrow {
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }
  .pain__heading:hover .pain__arrow {
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  /* ===== Right: Content Panels ===== */
  .pain__content {
    display: grid;
  }

  .pain__panel {
    grid-area: 1 / 1;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transform: translateY(8px);
    transition: opacity 0.4s ease, transform 0.4s ease;

    padding: 2rem 2.25rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3),
      0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
  }
  .pain__panel--active {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: auto;
    transform: translateY(0);
    border-color: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .pain__panel-title {
    font: 700 1.25rem/1.3 var(--font-body);
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .pain__panel-text {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  /* ===== Callout Boxes ===== */
  .pain__callout {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding: 0.875rem 1.125rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-cyan);
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.04);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .pain__callout--pink {
    border-left-color: var(--accent-pink);
    background: rgba(255, 45, 120, 0.04);
  }
  .pain__callout-label {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-right: 0.2rem;
  }

  /* ===== Bullet list ===== */
  .pain__bullets {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1rem 0 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .pain__bullets li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .pain__bullet-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--accent-pink);
    font-weight: 700;
    width: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .pain__bullets li strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  /* ===== Stat bar ===== */
  .pain__stat {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .pain__stat-number {
    font: 800 clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2rem)/1 var(--font-heading);
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    white-space: nowrap;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .pain__stat-label {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .pain__stat-source {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    opacity: 1;
  }

  /* ===== Transition: Die Lösung ===== */
  .pain__solution {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    padding: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem) 2rem;
    max-width: 680px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    overflow: visible;
  }

  .pain__solution-line {
    width: 2px;
    height: 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--accent-cyan));
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }

  .pain__solution-heading {
    font: 800 clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.25rem)/1.15 var(--font-heading);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .pain__solution-text {
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.1vw, 1rem);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .pain__solution-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.35);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .pain__solution-cta:hover {
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.06);
    border-color: var(--accent-cyan);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  /* Decorative hexagons */
  .pain__solution-deco {
    position: absolute;
    right: -80px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hex {
    display: block;
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
    clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 100% 25%, 100% 75%, 50% 100%, 0% 75%, 0% 25%);
    position: absolute;
  }
  .hex--1 { top: -50px; right: 0; opacity: 0.6; }
  .hex--2 { top: 0; right: 40px; width: 80px; height: 80px; opacity: 0.3; }
  .hex--3 { top: 40px; right: -20px; width: 50px; height: 50px; opacity: 0.15; }

  /* Accordion bodies: hidden on desktop, shown on mobile via mobile.css */
  .pain__accordion-body {
    display: none;
  }

  .pain__accordion-text {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding: 0.75rem 0 0 2.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pain__accordion-body {
      display: block;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 1023px) {
    .pain__content { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
    .pain__panel {
      opacity: 1;
      pointer-events: auto;
      transform: none;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .pain__panel:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .pain__solution-deco { display: none; }
  }

  /* ===== Ambient Glows ===== */
  .glow {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
    filter: blur(100px);
    animation: glowDrift 30s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }
  .glow--cyan {
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    top: -10%;
    right: -5%;
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
  }
  .glow--pink {
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    bottom: -15%;
    left: -8%;
    background: rgba(255, 45, 120, 0.04);
    animation-delay: -15s;
    animation-duration: 35s;
  }
  @keyframes glowDrift {
    0% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }
    50% { transform: translate(30px, -20px) scale(1.1); }
    100% { transform: translate(-20px, 15px) scale(0.95); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .glow { width: 300px; height: 300px; filter: blur(80px); }
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .glow { animation: none; }
  }
</style>
